document_data.name: Ithkur Onszibar
document_data.mainbody:
'''Ithkur Onszibar''' was a merchant from [[Amn]]. In [[1369 DR]] he traveled to [[Suzail]] in [[Cormyr]] in the search for a business partner to secure the eastern end of his trade route.
